@startuml
actor Patient
participant "System" as S
actor Staff
Patient -> S: Submit appointment request
altogether patient
  S -> S: Validate safety (no diagnosis/treatment/prescription)
  S -> S: Store appointment (status: Pending Review)
  S -> S: Check for conflicts with existing appointments
end
Patient <-- S: Confirmation
Staff -> S: View shared queue
S --> Staff: List of pending appointments
Staff -> S: Confirm or Cancel appointment
S -> S: Update status to Confirmed or Cancelled
Patient <-- S: Notification (if implemented)
@enduml
